```js
const cors = require('cors');

app.use(cors({
  origin: ['https://your-frontend.com'],  // Whitelist specific origins
  methods: ['GET'],
  allowedHeaders: ['Content-Type', 'Authorization'],
}));
```

---

### 🟠 MEDIUM — No Error Handling (OWASP A09: Security Logging and Monitoring Failures)

**Risk:** There is no global error handler. Unhandled errors will leak stack traces to clients in development mode (Express default), revealing internal paths, library versions, and code structure.

